FT  18 JUN 92 / Pit bid rejected
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
THE BID by redundant miners to buy Thurcroft colliery in South Yorkshire
appeared doomed last night after British Coal said the miners' offer to pay
less than a third of the cost of keeping the mine mothballed was
unacceptable.
