FT  18 JUN 92 / Nissan UK action ends
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
THE HIGH Court action in which Mr Stan Cholaj, a former assistant managing
director of Nissan UK, is suing the company for damages of more than Pounds
1m for wrongful dismissal and breach of contract ended yesterday. Judgment
is not expected before mid July.
