anticipated by the LRB and Shirayama which have not 'paid' Pounds 60m but by
all accounts have entered into an arrangement giving both parties the option
to withdraw.
It would probably help a depressed property market if Shirayama were given a
way out of a development whose financing in better times has already
defeated more experienced operators.
