WIGGINS TEAPE PENSIONS.
*****
Alastair Channing, deputy md of Associated British Ports, and James Shaw, md
of Grosvenor Square Properties, have both been appointed to the board of
ASSOCIATED BRITISH PORTS HOLDINGS.
*****
Michael Smith has been appointed to the board of BOWATER.
*****
Nicholas Hodges, md of LIG's European division, has been appointed a
director of LONDON INTERNATIONAL.
